title: Diaburo
description: Deer bath. Those who pull out the devil's bath will pull out their souls ... Yuna the devil appeared in front of the boy, Izumi Minamoto, who loves bathing and is a "Dear bath". Aiming at the "soul" that leaks from Izumi-kun's mouth, Yuna makes a naughty temptation with her hands! What will happen to the boy's peaceful bath life !?
author: Ohanachan
